Package training.capstone.pharma

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PatientRepository
    The PatientRepository interface provides data access methods for managing patient data in the database.
    PatientService
    The PatientService interface defines the contract for managing patient and user data and operations.
    UserRepository
    The UserRepository interface provides data access operations for managing user information in the database.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HomeController
    The HomeController class handles HTTP requests related to patients and orders.
    MedicinesEO
    The MedicinesEO class represents information about medicines.
    OrderEO
    The OrderEO class represents information about an order.
    PatientEO
    The PatientEO class represents information about a patient.
    PatientServiceImpl
    The PatientServiceImpl class implements the PatientService interface and provides the implementation for managing patient and user data and operations.
    PharmaPatientServiceApplication
    The PharmaPatientServiceApplication class is the main entry point for the Pharma Patient Service application.
    StatusEO
    The StatusEO class represents an entity for managing the status of an order associated with a patient.
    UserEO
    The UserEO class represents an entity for managing user information in the system.
